longBusinessSummary: Eviana Health Corporation produces and sells cannabinoid products from natural hemp strains of cannabis sativa for medical, beauty and grooming, vitamins and supplements, fitness, food and beverage, and pet markets. It is also involved in the growing of industrial hemp and extraction of cannabidiol. The company was formerly known as C&C Cosmeceuticals Corp. and changed its name to Eviana Health Corporation in May 2017. Eviana Health Corporation was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
